op_1756076707859.name: SKYSHIELD ACTIVE
op_1756076707859.objective:
PRESIDENTIAL FLIGHT (AF1) + ESCORT TRAFFIC OPERATING IN ATC24 AIRSPACE.  

AIRSPACE SECURITY REQUIREMENTS:  
- TFR ACTIVE 30NM RADIUS AROUND DESTINATION AERODROME.  
- ALL NON-PRESIDENTIAL TRAFFIC HOLD OR DIVERT.  
- NO PARALLEL APPROACHES OR DEPARTURES.  
- MINIMUM SEPARATION: 10NM LATERAL / 5000FT VERTICAL.  

ARRIVAL PROCEDURES:  
- AIR FORCE ONE GIVEN PRIORITY HANDLING.  
- LONGEST AVAILABLE RUNWAY ASSIGNED.  
- ESCORTS OPERATE IN FORMATION, SAME CLEARANCE BLOCK.  
- NO TAXI/PUSHBACK CLEARANCES ISSUED TO OTHER ACFT WHILE AF1 MOVING.  

DEPARTURE PROCEDURES:  
- AF1 EXPEDITED DEPARTURE, ESCORTS CLEARED WITH AF1.  
- AIRSPACE REMAINS STERILE UNTIL AF1 >30NM FROM AD.
op_1756076707859.notes: ATC REMARKS:   - FREQUENCY DISCIPLINE REQUIRED.   - NO NONESSENTIAL TRANSMISSIONS DURING OPS.   - CIVILIAN ACFT EXPECT DIVERSION OR HOLD INSTRUCTIONS.
